HEADWORD: Title-page
<hw>Ti"tle-page`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The page of a
book which contains it title.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The world's all <qex>title-page</qex>; there's no contents.</q>
<rj><qau>Young.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Titler</ent>⟦br⟧
